# Scaffold .gitignore for a HACS Lovelace card (frontend-only).
# Mirrors the unified portfolio baseline (verified byte-identical
# across the user's six *-austria integration repos as of 2026-05-08)
# — adapted for a card-only repo with two card-specific tweaks:
#
#   1. `dist/` is NOT ignored. For a standalone HACS plugin the
#      single-file bundle at dist/<card>.js IS the artefact users
#      install — it must stay tracked. (For a HACS *integration* repo
#      the card bundle lives at custom_components/<domain>/www/<card>.js
#      and `dist/` would be ignored as Python packaging output.)
#   2. The Python blocks below match nothing in this repo but stay in
#      place — keeps the file aligned with the portfolio baseline so
#      copy-paste between repos doesn't lose protections.
#
# IMPORTANT: review before committing. Loosen only with intention.
#
# Two load-bearing rules:
#   1. `.claude/` ignores any per-project Claude state and project-level
#      skills so they never land in git. User-level rules live in
#      ~/.claude/skills/.
#   2. `package-lock.json` is intentionally NOT here. It MUST stay
#      committed so reproducible card builds work in CI.

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Python (kept for portfolio-baseline parity; not used in this repo)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyc
*$py.class
*.so
.Python

.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.tox/

*.egg-info/
.eggs/
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.python-version
.HA_VERSION
uv.lock

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Node / JS / TypeScript
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
.npm/
*.js.map

# Bundler caches
.rollup.cache/
.vite-cache/
.parcel-cache/

# Note: dist/ is intentionally NOT ignored — it's the published bundle.

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OS metadata
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini
Desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.bak

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IDE / editor state
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
.cursor/
.cursorrules.local
.continue/
.windsurf/

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI assistants — local state, transcripts, plans, project-level skills
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.claude/
.claude/skills/
.claude-cache/
.claude-*
.aider*

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Static analysis tooling
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.fallow/
.fallowrc.json
.fallowrc.jsonc
fallow.toml

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Secrets / credentials — NEVER commit
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.secrets
*.secret
secrets.json
secrets.yaml
auth.json
credentials.json
token.json
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HA local state — logs, config copies (kept for parity)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.storage/
home-assistant.log*
home-assistant_*.log*
*.log
config/

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Personal dev tooling — push/sync scripts targeting a dev box, scratch
# Each contributor wires these up locally; nothing under scripts/ is
# shared via git.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
scripts/
dev-push.sh
dev/
test/
target/

# Personal notes / scratch — *.local.md is the convention
CLAUDE.local.md
*.local.md
local_*.py
private_*.py
